{"tid":1808912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不忘沙士一疫  好好保護自己]","createTime":"2020-01-02T16:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T17:05:00.000Z","uid":236080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a62ebad739cd6c12804d80507910fb95c2e8b55","tid":1808912,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"我知道推行動po重要 但武漢不明肺炎都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家成日講<span style=\"color: red;\">要保命</span>不被捕 先可以係煲底<span style=\"color: red;\">除低口罩</span>相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要明白, 病毒唔係講笑, 唔好話用病毒攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住<span style=\"color: blue;\">病毒殺人係唔會分對象</span>, 無論小朋友, 年青人, 成年人, 長者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當內地甚至港府都未確定會唔會人傳人<br />\n但係: <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1) 武漢當地有部分感染者聲稱事前並無食野味<br />\n2) 武漢當地海鮮市場附近小區都有人感染</span><br />\n以上可見, 未有結果下唔可以100% 否認人傳人,<br />\n現時肯定嘅只係病毒並非03年沙士, 但大家要更小心, 因為病毒係新出現, 嚴重性, 醫治方法全部未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要引起恐慌 <span style=\"color: red;\">但都唔可以掉以輕心</span><br />\n<br />\n係內地政府 / 香港政府未有任何公佈<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 100%</span></span> 肯定病毒係無事前,<br />\n為咗自己同屋企人, 為咗小朋友, 咩都好....<br />\n聽日開始盡可能做以下嘅事:<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1) 去人多地方 (公共交通工具,空氣唔流通嘅室內等), 戴上口罩<br />\n2) 掂到公共設施(扶手, 升降機按鈕, 大廈密碼鎖等) 唔好摸眼耳口鼻及進食, 並應該盡快洗手<br />\n3) 盡可能帶備酒精消毒搓手液/紙巾<br />\n4) 自己, 家人或朋友 有任何上呼吸感染症狀, 無論有冇去過內地都要盡快求醫<br />\n5) 食嘢飲嘢盡量唔好同人share口水尾<br />\n6) 唔好自私, 咳要用手um住個口</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求下大家<br />\n要好好保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d231f3f064e0b62102600b21f557b3d206b55e3f","tid":1808912,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人見到 聽日開始注意個人衛生 要比日常更留意!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0233150ac616104dbe1b5a41af3183cf64bc441d","tid":1808912,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaftTAw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaftTAw.png&h=bc839024&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76b8773284c760664470cc2f913367792a953b8e","tid":1808912,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0233150ac616104dbe1b5a41af3183cf64bc441d","tid":1808912,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaftTAw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaftTAw.png&h=bc839024&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勤洗手 咪做傳染病嘅幕後黑手"},{"pid":"e2f6443c68b3e930512dfc4ac2df9794b68af47b","tid":1808912,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"人人做齊個6點 <br />\n抗疫就贏咗9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332522e2001924333989a8b383be38654f05ca04","tid":1808912,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"暴力面前尚可留力<br />\n病毒面前是零憐憫"},{"pid":"be414ef357fe95